    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7">3. The third step is a quick tip from what I’ve observed works for me when trying to understand research papers. The third step is to take structured notes that summarises the key discoveries, findings and techniques within a paper, in your own words.</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content7 cid-ttbhFZC4Ql" id="content7-8" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
